sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as machine-ui
    participant BC as BuyController GET /api/buy/status/:charge_id
    participant Mem as order_statuses (in-memory)
    participant DB as MySQL orders.status
    participant Om as Omise (optional)

    loop จนกว่าจะ terminal
        UI->>BC: GET status
        BC->>Mem: lookup charge_id
        alt มีใน memory
            Mem-->>BC: pending_payment | paid | ...
        else ไม่มีใน memory
            BC->>DB: SELECT status by charge_id
            BC->>Om: Charge.retrieve ถ้า DB ยัง pending\nแต่ Omise successful
            Om-->>BC: charge object
            BC->>BC: อาจ trigger _execute_dispense\nเมื่อ reconcile
        end
        BC-->>UI: status JSON
    end
